{"tha-ap179:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap179:0.2":"Kumudavagga ","tha-ap179:0.3":"Ekadipiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap179:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa munino, ","tha-ap179:1.2":"salale bodhimuttame; ","tha-ap179:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap179:1.4":"ekadipam adasaham. ","tha-ap179:2.1":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap179:2.2":"nibbatte punnasancaye; ","tha-ap179:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap179:2.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap179:3.1":"Solase kappasahasse, ","tha-ap179:3.2":"ito te caturo jana; ","tha-ap179:3.3":"Candabha nama namena, ","tha-ap179:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap179:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap179:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap179:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap179:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekadipiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap179:6.1":"Ekadipiyattherassapadanam sattamam. ","tha-ap179:6.2":"Navamam bhanavaram. "}